data.description: *** Large Price Reduction *** Charming 2-bed, 2-bath home in a secure gated golf community beckons with comfort and convenience. Enjoy the allure of low HOA fees while indulging in an array of community amenities: poolside relaxation, billiards, sauna serenity, invigorating exercise options, a literary escape in the library, and delightful dining at the on-site restaurant. Embrace an active lifestyle with shuffleboard, tennis, and the pristine golf course at your doorstep. This property seamlessly combines modern living with a vibrant community spirit, offering a perfect blend for your next chapter.   ****New Roof May 2023, *** Carpet Nov, 2023   ****  Some Furniture & Furnishings are negotiable. *** Glass mirrior attached to living room wall (not the one framed conveys) will stay with home.
